---
title: Roasted Chicken & Pumpkin Bengali Biryani with Yoghurt & Coriander
description: Curry on rice is all well and good, but when the rice itself is cooked with the curry paste? Now that’s magical. Studded with aromatic spices and roasted pumpkin, this dish packs flavour in every bite.

